snippet.title: eFootball™ CONNECT: Spotlight Interview / Global
snippet.description:
【Survey for eFootball™ CONNECT: Spotlight Interview】
https://www.smartsurvey.co.uk/s/ZHIHE1/

We have released new content where our General Director and General Producer directly respond to many of the comments and feedback we’ve received from our users.

The eFootball™ team will continue to review all kinds of improvements while taking into account the feedback provided by users.
We will also steadily attend to the following matters that were not discussed in the eFootball™ CONNECT: Spotlight Interview broadcast from 4 February.

① Unauthorised Acquisition or Dissemination of Game Data
Unauthorised access of a server operated by KONAMI and unauthorised acquisition or dissemination of confidential in-game data are actions that violate the Terms of Use for this game.
Such actions may also violate the applicable laws of your country or region (such as the Act on the Prohibition of Unauthorized Computer Access in Japan).
In the event that an illicit act is discovered, we will enforce strict punishments such as the following measures, as required. 
・ Temporary or permanent suspension of the eFootball™ game account involved in that act
・ Ban on participation in official eSports competitions
・ Legal action
Please note that the dissemination of data acquired through unauthorised means is also an action that violates the Terms of Use.
We are currently implementing system improvements aimed at preventing the unauthorised access of in-game data.
We ask for your understanding and cooperation so that we can maintain a safe environment where all users can play with peace of mind.

② Smart Assist
We added the Smart Assist feature so that more users, including beginners, can easily experience the fun and exhilaration of eFootball™ matches.
We are currently receiving wide-ranging feedback from users regarding Smart Assist, and we will continue to look into further updates.
From the summer of 2026, we are planning to test PvP matches that will allow users to limit matchmaking to whoever is playing with Smart Assist turned either on or off.
We will continue to examine ways to build an ideal environment that allows all users to enjoy themselves freely, whether playing with or without Smart Assist. We would greatly appreciate it if you could continue to share your feedback to meet this aim.


Stay tuned to the eFootball™ accounts:
Youtube: / playefootball
Instagram: / efootball
X: / play_efootball
Facebook: / playefootball
#efootball   #esports #football #soccer #konami

snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Everybody wants this. 

Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1. Watch the full trailer now. 

Almost 20 years after making their iconic turn as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel—Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as “Lily” and “Irv” from the first film. 
 
“The Devil Wears Prada 2” is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and Aline Brosh McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1.

snippet.title: Danmusa New Prince - Aure (Performance Video)
snippet.description:
The Ultimate Wedding Soundtrack is Here!

Experience the magic of love with "Aure," the highly anticipated EP from Danmusa New Prince. This 4-track collection is expertly crafted for the modern wedding dinner, blending soulful melodies with the rhythmic heartbeat of celebration. Whether it’s the couple’s grand entrance or the final dance of the night, "Aure" provides the perfect atmosphere for your special day.

Artist: Danmusa New Prince 
Title: Aure
Video Director: Northern Light Productions
Label: 360 Music World 
Copyright: © 2026 360 Music World. 
Licensing: Under Exclusive License to Ash Music Entertainment. 
Distribution: All rights reserved.

SONG LYRICS:

[Intro]

Yace yar uwata
Tace dan uwana
Yace kinyo sifar larabawa

Its dj tune on the beat

[first verse]

Ni naga ni naga auren soyayya
Yau andaura
Ina amarya chemata ga ango
Abakin kofa
Yazo ya bude fuska
Don kallonta
Yazam kaman al'ada
Shi agurinsa
Tunda aure babban bautane
In an raya
Kunga lada bansan qarshe ba
Babbar sunnah
Masu qaryar chewa anfasa to andaura
kunyi qarya dama kunsaba da abun kunya
Ga amarya ga ango mukam munayin waka
Inda ankai auren soyayya sai mun leqa
Yanzu kundau sabon alqibla na hangen nesa
Inyace eh karda kiche a'a to dan Allah
Kaji ango kaima saurara saika duba
Tunda mata ance rauninsu ba qaryaba
Babu zagi ango ba duka mata taka
Tazamo ma tamkar aljannah che a gidanka
Yanzu rana dai tuni ta nuna yau munganta
Auyi aure auren soyayya bana fushiba

[first verse]

Keche yaga yaga yaga yaga ke ya gani
Kamar wasa
Kunsan lamarinsu
Yabi ciki haka ta jiki da jini
Ango da amarya burinsu sugansu suna
Rawa rawa irin juyin dan mazari
Yau ranar kuche to kusha shagalinku
Maza maza maza ango taho gida
Faka faka faka amarya ganinka takeso
Liki liki liki akache amaryaa
Biki biki biki zokuje daukar hoto da ango
Rana rana tazo shikenan gidan angonki
Zaki jeki chan zaki sauka Allah shike iko
Gani gani gani karsu miki amarya
Kinfi kinfi kinfi qarfin raini suji da Allah
Kafi kafi kafi ango kafi kaima
Kafi kafi kafi qarfin raini wallahi ango

[Hook]

(Yace yar uwata)
(Tace dan uwana)
(Yace kinyo sifar larabawa)

Yace yar uwata
Tace dan uwana
Yace kinyo sifar larabawa

snippet.title: [Official Trailer] MuTeLuv ตอน 9 วัด ปะล่ะ Love Me if You Swear
snippet.description:
เมื่อ “ตั้ม” (เซิร์ฟ พชร) หัวหน้าแก๊งเหนืออินทร์ ที่เพิ่งได้ตำแหน่งมาสดๆ ร้อนๆ จากการ ‘มู’ ดันซวยจัดๆ เพราะโดน “โอ๋” (จาว่า พบธรรม) หัวหน้าแก๊งปทุมไพศาล แย่งตราประจำแก๊งไป จนทำให้เพื่อนในแก๊งเริ่มสงสัยในความสามารถของตั้มว่าคู่ควรกับตำแหน่งรึเปล่า
 พอตั้มนึกดีๆ ทั้งหมดเป็นเพราะตัวเองไปมูไว้แล้วไม่ได้แก้บน ภารกิจแก้บน 9 วัดของตั้มจึงได้เริ่มขึ้น แต่ความซวยก็ไม่เคยพัก ดันมาเจอกับโอ๋ที่มาแก้บน 9 วัดเหมือนกัน ทั้งสองคนจึงได้ออกเดินทางแก้บนไปพร้อมๆ กัน
 การแก้บนครั้งนี้จากคู่ปรับ เปลี่ยนเป็นคู่บุญ และจะกลายเป็นคู่กันมั้ย มาติดตามเรื่องราวได้ใน “MuTeLuv ตอน 9 วัด ปะล่ะ Love Me if You Swear” ทุกวันจันทร์ เวลา 20:30 น. ทางช่อง GMM25 และทางแอปพลิเคชั่น TrueVisions NOW เท่านั้น เริ่มตอนแรก 9 กุมภาพันธ์นี้

กำกับซีรีส์ : สุวนันท์ โพธิ์กุดไสย์

snippet.title: Fast & Furious 11 (2026) - Vin Diesel, Dwayne Johnson, Jason Statham | Concept Trailer
snippet.description:
#FastAndFurious11 #VinDiesel #DwayneJohnson

Watch This Fast & Furious 11 Fan Made Concept Trailer

Vin Diesel's Dom Toretto must ultimately confront his destiny as the Fast & Furious franchise approaches its explosive conclusion, with every main character coming together for one last ride that takes place around the world and pushes the limits of physics the series has already pushed. Dom has taken down international crime syndicates and government conspiracy after ten movies; however, he finds himself facing the only foe that cannot be outrun – his past in the form of foes who have come together specifically to destroy the family that has endured impossible odds through sheer willpower and quarter mile loyalty. Dwayne Johnson will return to the role of Luke Hobbs after years of on-screen tension with Vin Diesel as Hobbs comes to the aid of Dom for the final time since the stakes have grown too large for the family to overcome on its own. Jason Statham's Deckard Shaw completes the three-man team of the most elite warriors that must work together when a new foe emerges with the resources and ferocity of the previous villains were mere speed bumps.

The level of action goes completely overboard with both practical stunts and CGI spectacle combining for a variety of set pieces including cars being dropped from space, highways filled with military vehicles and Dom performing stunts that would be deemed impossible in previous films. There will be true emotional depth as characters that began as street racers and are now globe-trotting heroes face mortality and legacy, asking themselves if their chosen family will survive the final war intact. The competitive energy channeled into mutual respect by Vin Diesel, Dwayne Johnson and Jason Statham due to their experience working together as a team to face danger together shows that sometimes the best teams are formed from individuals who have been adversaries at some point in the past. The reason why this movie is unique is because it understands that everything eventually comes to an end – the film provides massive spectacle while also paying tribute to the individual character arcs developed over twenty years and brings back many faces you may have forgotten existed for moments that truly warrant nostalgia rather than using it for fan service.

Expect cameos from all previous films, returns that serve the story rather than providing a simple cameo fan service and a sendoff that proves family is more than just based on blood – it's the people that you choose to ride with you no matter where the road takes you and no matter how impossible the odds are and how much destruction there is to your name.

Disclaimer: 
This is an unofficial fan-made concept trailer made solely for the purpose of entertainment and artistry. It is not related to nor sponsored by Universal Pictures or any other party having the rights to the Fast & Furious franchise. All rights to the original characters, story and intellectual property belong to their respective owners. This video utilizes artificial intelligence generated images and editing techniques to provide a visual representation of a hypothetical eleventh installment.
